              h3 Contemporary
              p Drawing on classical, modern and jazz dance styles, contemporary dance has evolved to incorporate many characteristics of a broader range of dance forms.
              img(src = "https://www.shutterstock.com/image-photo/young-african-american-male-dancer-600nw-2484208575.jpg")
              a(href = "/enroll")
