            div.card
              h3 Hip-Hop
              p Hip-hop dancing refers to a range of street dances that developed in relation to hip hop music and culture. 
              img(src = "https://t3.ftcdn.net/jpg/04/16/77/72/360_F_416777220_1wLyOwwSXAHJRCQbylVIXif3exe2X3gP.jpg")
              a(href = "/enroll")
