                  | Join Now
            div.card
              h3 Ballroom
              p Dances within these categories include the waltz, tango and foxtrot, and pasodoble, bolero and samba.
              img(src = "https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcS3JGmivArDS3rbNBv2PLAz-Gc_oY_L7QRcMQ&s")
              a(href = "/enroll")
                button(class = "btn")
                  | Join Now
            div.card
              h3 Tap Dancing
              p Often performed as part of musical theatre, tap dancing often focuses on choreography and formations, with more than one tap dancer performing at once.
              img(src = "https://t3.ftcdn.net/jpg/12/65/86/52/360_F_1265865233_Lh1MX1UsNUfz8Ji8jigjdcXzJJSnaSAJ.jpg")
