                button(class = "btn")
                  | Join Now
            div.card
              h3  Folk Dance
              p Folk dancing is celebrated worldwide with people of different cultures and religions using various forms of folk dance to portray emotions, even aspects of daily life.
              img(src = "https://t4.ftcdn.net/jpg/00/84/09/49/360_F_84094964_qotli3Xd9fkFb41IaRqrt268VtexRpM8.jpg")

